Fuel Welcome Offer: Must be a registered 7Rewards member to participate. Members use fuel promotional savings in 7-Eleven App or at the pump by selecting 7Rewards and entering phone number to get 11 cents off every gallon (up to 20 gal). 11 cents off promotional savings valid for the first 90 days or 7 trips, whichever comes first; member will then get 3 cents off per gallon (up to 20 gal).